high_descs: Turn to your left walking partly to the stove then turning right to face the counter.
Walk towards the counter and pick up the lettuce.
Turn around take a step and turn left then a quick right to face the sink at the end of the counter.
Turn slightly to place the lettuce in the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and take the lettuce back out.
Turn left and walk towards the counter.
Place the lettuce on the counter in front of the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Clean the lettuce to place on the counter in front of the coffee machine.

high_descs: Walk to the left a little.
grab the cabbage on the counter
turn right, walk to the sink
put the cabbage in the sink, wash the cabbage, take the cabbage out
turn left, walk to the counter with a coffee machine on it
put the cabbage on the counter
anns.task_desc: Wash the cabbage in the sink, put the cabbage on the counter

high_descs: Move to the left and stand at the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick the head of lettuce up from the counter.
Go to the right and stand in front of the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink, turn the water on and then off, and then pick the lettuce up from the sink.
Go to the left and stand in front of the counter in front of the coffee maker.
Put the lettuce down on the counter in front of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean head of lettuce on the counter.
